'''''Mythos''': Rivista di Storia delle Religioni'' is an annual [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[academic journal]] published by Giuseppe Sciascia Editore on behalf of the [[University of Palermo]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.worldcat.org/title/mythos/oclc/35805913 |title=Mythos. (Journal, magazine, 1989) |publisher=[[WorldCat]] |work= |accessdate=2012-04-24}}</ref> It was established in 1989 by Giuseppe Martorana,<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.testlettere.unipa.it/?id_pagina=617;id_menu_pre=611 |title=Mythos |publisher=Facoltà di Lettere e Filosofia - Università di Palermo |work= |accessdate=2012-04-24}}</ref> with a new series started in 2007.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.testlettere.unipa.it/?id_pagina=620&id_menu_pre=611 |title=Mythos - La nuova serie |publisher=Facoltà di Lettere e Filosofia - Università di Palermo |work= |accessdate=2012-04-24}}</ref> It reviews religious [[narrative]] and [[mythos]] in Italian, French, English, German, and Spanish. The current [[editors-in-chief]] are Nicola Cusumano (University of Palermo) and Corinne Bonnet ([[University of Toulouse]]).

